Abstract-A-TAK

This project is a restructuring of TAK Product Center's official "helloworld"
example ATAK plugin, reorganized so a single branch builds for every supported
ATAK version (4.10–5.8) instead of one maintenance branch per version.

The original HelloWorld plugin and the ATAK-CIV SDK it targets are works of the
TAK Product Center, distributed under the Apache License, Version 2.0. This
repository continues under that license (see LICENSE).

The ATAK SDK jars (sdk/main-*.jar) are obtained separately from the official
ATAK-CIV releases and are not distributed here.
